cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper is about semantic image segmentation, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper proposes a new network module for semantic segmentation, which involves learning region consistency at different levels. This suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM), as these fields often involve developing new models or algorithms for image analysis.
